        "TileImage": "$($repository 73f1046e-7c74-42b6-b4a7-7e4dd34f25af).Image",
        "Description": "We are almost there 47, this target is actually a team.  A team of skilled hackers who serve as the prime asset in Armaxia&apos;s intel gathering team. The Data Core from New York pointed us at a large Farm i n Colorado, and it seems to be one of Armaxia&apos;s secret training facilities.  Terminate the hacker team and anyone else who gets in your way. You are cleared for any ammount of collateral damage you deal.  This is a hornet&apos;s nest 47, be VERY alert and watch your back at all times.",
